---
[v2] arch: arm64: dts: mt7988: extend WiFi wmcpu reserved memory to 10M

Update and extend the wmcpu WiFi reserved memory to 10MB in the mt7988 DTS
to support new firmware design improvements and enhanced WiFi firmware
EMI (External Memory Interface) applications.

---
v2: Change the base address of wmcpu-reserved to 0x4e600000
v1: Update mt7988.dtsi to extend WiFi reserved memory to 10M
---


--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt7988a.dtsi
@@ -157,8 +157,8 @@
 			no-map;
 		};
 
-		wmcpu_emi: wmcpu-reserved@47cc0000 {
-			reg = <0 0x47cc0000 0 0x00100000>;
+		wmcpu_emi: wmcpu-reserved@4e600000 {
+			reg = <0 0x4e600000 0 0xa00000>;
 			no-map;
 		};
 
